{"tid":2237603,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"（有無心理治療師）發覺自己有時好易唔知點解會燥底","createTime":"2020-10-10T11:59:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-10T12:57:52.000Z","uid":278102,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"68ce048e2eb496add1d3fce7a01f8b85ed6d204b","tid":2237603,"uid":278102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T11:59:19.000Z","msg":"明明平時自己好好脾氣既，可能係自我感覺良好啦&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係唔知點解硬係會有啲時候因為啲好小既事（甚至可能明明乜事都無發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）而莫名地感到好燥底好想嬲好想搵啲嘢發洩咁<br />\n好似強迫症<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我覺得咁樣好辛苦，成日同自己講要冷靜但係越諗就越冷靜唔到&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77763e47188c867ac8cb719211a7e4a0fbf21678","tid":2237603,"uid":195815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T12:00:00.000Z","msg":"me too<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b656a112b52f58cef612aa9f6a49b75822d0a23d","tid":2237603,"uid":55493,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T12:01:22.000Z","msg":"放心，燥底係人之常情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb19821840fcfa5c0d120d77b454ede6cb80c40d","tid":2237603,"uid":278102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77763e47188c867ac8cb719211a7e4a0fbf21678","tid":2237603,"uid":195815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T12:00:00.000Z","msg":"me too<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T12:02:46.000Z","msg":"咁樣真係好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果話有源頭解決就話姐，但係真係唔知點解就係無啦啦好心煩好想發洩咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3f5c8e6a391c4e16a2004d7d83b3a9dcccaec5e","tid":2237603,"uid":112901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB